#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:2
msgid "Script Structure"
msgstr "脚本结构"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:4
msgid ""
"Let's learn how to program your OpenMV Cam now! Note that this tuturial "
"assumes you know how the python language works. If you don't know how "
"python works please study up on it. There are plenty of web tuturials "
"about how to write python code (finally, if you know any other C like "
"programming language you can pick up python easily since it's VERY "
"similar)."
msgstr ""
"现在让我们学习如何编程您的 OpenMV Cam！请注意，本教程假设您知道 python "
"语言的工作原理。如果您不了解 python 的工作原理，请先学习。有很多关于如何编写 "
"python 代码的网络教程（最后，如果您了解其他类似 C 的编程语言，"
"您可以轻松地学习 python，因为它们非常相似）。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:10
msgid "Anyway, any script you write is going to have three distinct parts::"
msgstr "无论如何，您编写的任何脚本都将包含三个不同的部分::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:23
msgid ""
"The first part of your OpenMV Cam code should include some header "
"comments, import statements to bring modules into scope, and finally "
"constants and global variables in your code."
msgstr "您 OpenMV Cam 代码的第一部分应包括一些头部注释、导入语句将模块引入范围，以及"
"最后在代码中定义常量和全局变量。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:27
msgid ""
"Next, you're going to want to do one-time setup code. This includes "
"things like creating I/O pin objects, setting up the camera, defining "
"helper functions, etc."
msgstr "接下来，您将需要进行一次性设置代码。这包括创建 I/O "
"引脚对象、设置相机、定义辅助函数等。"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:31
msgid ""
"Finally, you'll create a ``while(True):`` loop under which you'll put all"
" code that gets called in a loop repeatedly until power-off."
msgstr "最后，您将创建一个 ``while(True):`` 循环，在该循环下，您将放置所有需要重复调"
"用的代码在一个循环中，直到关闭电源为止。"

