msgid "Here's an example of this::"
msgstr "以下是一个示例::"

#: ../../openmvcam/tutorial/script_structure.rst:60
msgid ""
"Note that if you do not have an infinite while loop in your code then "
"once your OpenMV Cam finishes running the script it will sit there and do"
" nothing."
msgstr "请注意，如果您的代码中没有无限循环，则一旦您的 OpenMV Cam "
"完成运行脚本，它将停在那里并且什么都不做。"
